GetQuestByIdQueryHandler ..> GetQuestByIdQuery : Uses
GetQuestByIdQueryHandler --> IQuestRepository
GetQuestByIdQueryHandler --> IQuestStepRepository
GetQuestByIdQueryHandler ..> QuestDetailsDto : Returns
@enduml